\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 Covariates\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Data were collected on age, sex, body mass index (BMI), dietary habits, physical activity, smoking status, alcohol consumption, medication use (including antidepressants), and perceived stress. These variables were included as covariates in statistical analyses.\
